From Clint Eastwood:
"I love it when people call Trump stupid..." You mean the billionaire who beat up all Democrats, buried 16 career Republican politicians and continues to ridicule media that were once respectable...
You mean the guy who won the presidency?
You mean the guy with the supermodel wife?
You mean the guy whose words drastically stopped illegal border crossings?
You mean the guy whose mere presence made the stock market break records?
You mean the guy who created a million jobs in his first 7 months in office? Are you sure you know what you're resisting?.
Are you sure you support a party that allows the destruction of all fundamental principles of Christianity?.
Are you sure you support a party that voted 100% against the abolition of slavery?.
Are you sure you're really serious about politics like Maxine Waters?.
Are you sure you don't see anything wrong with someone who has.. 40 year career as a public servant living in a $4.5 mansion representing a district she doesn't even live in?
Surely you don't see anything wrong or peculiar about Hillary Clinton, a woman involved in politics for the last 30 years and with a net worth of $240 million?
Surely he doesn't base his opinion on the hate spread by a corrupt, paid for media platform?.
Could you tell me five things the Democratic Party has done to improve their daily prosperity as a working American citizen?.
Probably not...
Do you realize the mess you are sending your children to once they are adults by continuing to support a political party that has done nothing for the poor, except keep them poor, give them free abortions and a few hundred a month to keep food in their refrigerators ?
The prosperity and safety of its citizens is the primary responsibility of your government.
Join the program!
Everyone else has failed him terribly!
Be smart and take a stand for the sake of your children. I promise you a country full of illegal immigrants, abortions, $15 an hour jobs, and people without gender will not make your country or your life any more prosperous.
Rosie, Madonna, Katy Perry and Robert De Niro are not like you. They don't have to live through the everyday inequality of the average American.
Men don’t hate women, white people don’t hate black and Donald Trump isn’t racist.
Stop allowing yourself to be brainwashed by a game that has continuously failed you.
Take care of your prosperity, your safety, your children and an "America First" mentality.
Abandon these corrupt politicians who have hindered your growth.
Abandon these corrupt politicians who have prevented your children from growing up.
Be stronger, take a stand and act like a proud American.
Notice the spirit of Trump-supporting, freedom-loving Americans and imagine where we would be as a country if we all had the same priorities.
